Changed the old and outdated romanizations to Wiki-Standard. Many chinese and korean martial arts practitioneers usually refuse that. It's not Choi Hong Hi/Hong-Hi anymore but [[Choi Hong-hi]] instead. Many first names in the articel still used the old romanitazion (capitalize the second syllable, like Sun Yat-Sen instead of [[Sun Yat-sen]]). Now all names are  on Wiki standard. [[Doc-Fai Wong]] is the only exception since he himself prefers it. Doc-fai Wong would "technically" be correct

Unsourced information: this citation can't be used to support the claim "Choy Li Fut is an effective self-defense system".  The contents are controversial and possible fictional.  The book references Choy Li Fut in only a handful of places, anecdotally.
